Package: netmetaviz
Title: Visualization Tools for Network Meta-Analysis
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R:
    person("Yuki", "Furukawa",
           email = "furukawa.y.psy@gmail.com",
           role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0002-0897-8339"))
Description: Provides visualization tools for network meta-analysis (NMA)
    results from the 'netmeta' package. Includes functions for creating
    color-coded league tables (using CINeMA evidence confidence ratings),
    Kilim plots (multi-outcome summary tables), Vitruvian plots (absolute
    effect visualizations), and minimally contextualized evidence frameworks.
